<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Silver Oak University | Education to Innovation</title>
    <style>
          
* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
}


body {
    
    background-image: url('campus.jpg'); 
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-attachment: fixed;
    height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    color: #ffffff;
    overflow-x: hidden;
}


.bg-overlay {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: rgba(14, 34, 18, 0.65); 
    z-index: 1;
}

.navbar {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 20px 8%;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
}

.logo-text {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    color: #f1f1f1;
    border-left: 4px solid #4caf50; /* Signature green highlight border */
    padding-left: 10px;
}

.nav-links a {
    color: #ffffff;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-left: 30px;
    font-weight: 400;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
}

.nav-links a:hover {
    color: #81c784; 
}


.hero-section {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    flex-grow: 1;
}

.hero-content {
    max-width: 800px;
}

.motto {
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #a5d6a7;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
}

.hero-section h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
}

.description {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 35px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #e0e0e0;
}


.cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 20px;
}

.btn {
    padding: 12px 30px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 25px;
    transition: transform 0.2s;
}

.btn-primary {
    background: #4caf50;
    color: #ffffff;
}

.btn-primary:hover {
    background: #388e3c;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: #ffffff;
    border: 2px solid #ffffff;
}

.btn-secondary:hover {
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #111111;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
}


.info-footer {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-around;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    background: rgba(14, 23, 15, 0.9);
    padding: 20px 5%;
    border-top: 3px solid #4caf50;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
}

.footer-item {
    margin: 5px 15px;
    color: #d1d1d1;
}


@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .navbar {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 15px;
    }
    .nav-links a {
        margin: 0 10px;
    }
    .hero-section h1 {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
    }
    .cta-buttons {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
    }
    .info-footer {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
        gap: 10px;
    }
}

    </style>
</head>
<body>

   
    <div class="bg-overlay"></div>

   
    <header class="navbar">
        <div class="logo-container">
            <span class="logo-text">SILVER OAK UNIVERSITY</span>
        </div>
        <nav class="nav-links">
            <a href="https://silveroakuni.ac.in/" target="_blank">Home</a>
            <a href="https://silveroakuni.ac.in/program-offered" target="_blank">Programs</a>
            <a href="https://silveroakuni.ac.in/admission" target="_blank">Admissions</a>
            <a href="https://silveroakuni.ac.in/contact" target="_blank">Contact Us</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

  
    <main class="hero-section">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <p class="motto">"Gyanam Parmam Bhushnam"</p>
            <h1>Education to Innovation</h1>
            <p class="description">
                Join one of the premier private universities in Ahmedabad, Gujarat, fostering deep academic standards, state-of-the-art infrastructure, and strong industry integration.
            </p>
            <div class="cta-buttons">
                <a href="https://silveroakuni.ac.in/admission" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">Apply Online Now</a>
                <a href="https://silveroakuni.ac.in/program-offered" class="btn btn-secondary" target="_blank">Explore Programs</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

   
    <footer class="info-footer">
        <div class="footer-item">
            <strong>📍 Location:</strong> Gota, Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India - 382481
        </div>
        <div class="footer-item">
            <strong>✉️ Email:</strong> info@silveroakuni.ac.in
        </div>
        <div class="footer-item">
            <strong>📞 Call:</strong> +91 079-66046300
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
